quiz_1_feedback_1.eng: It is great to hear you are feeling positive today. Your presence makes a real difference for your family!

quiz_1_feedback_2.eng: Life has its great and hard moments – that is okay. You are on the right track.

quiz_1_feedback_3.eng: It is normal to have hard days as a parent. Take a deep breath and know you are not alone!

quiz_1_feedback_4.eng: It is normal to have stressful days as a parent. You are not alone! Reach out to someone supportive if you need to talk.

quiz_1_feedback_5.eng: It is normal to feel tired some days as a parent. Close your eyes for a few minutes to get some rest.
